snippet.title: Zombies Overloaded Official Trailer
snippet.description:
ZOMBIES!!! Overloaded waves of undead chaos! Armed with crazy weapons and power-ups, you’ll fight, dodge, and nuke your way through endless hordes. Face intense bosses, survive outrageous room filling hordes, and climb the leaderboards! It’s fast, it’s for gory, it’s OVERLOADED!!

Wishlist Zombies Overloaded on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/3446070/Zombies_Overloaded/
